I've checked it already, and it's very accurate.

24
00:01:57,000 --> 00:02:00,280
It's just like you, growing stronger with age.

25
00:02:01,680 --> 00:02:02,980
Good stuff.

26
00:02:02,980 --> 00:02:06,580
Yunzheng, you know me so well.

27
