307
00:18:41,040 --> 00:18:44,800
Looks like my weekend is destined to be spent in the duty room.

308
00:18:44,800 --> 00:18:46,402
She has an appointment?

309
00:18:46,402 --> 00:18:47,902
Yes.

310
00:18:50,680 --> 00:18:52,620
