334
00:20:30,640 --> 00:20:32,560
Don't get me wrong.

335
00:20:44,880 --> 00:20:47,420
 Look how time flies. We haven't seen each other for so long.

336
00:20:47,420 --> 00:20:49,140
That's right.

337
00:20:49,140 --> 00:20:51,520
- It's been quite long. 
