340
00:20:56,300 --> 00:20:58,220
Look how fast time passes.

341
00:20:58,220 --> 00:21:00,980
In the blink of an eye, she has grown into a big girl.

342
00:21:00,980 --> 00:21:02,580
She was so little back then.

343
00:21:02,580 --> 00:21:04,920
