359
00:21:46,420 --> 00:21:47,360
I see.

360
00:21:47,360 --> 00:21:49,640
He's the marketing director.

361
00:21:49,640 --> 00:21:50,920
And he's usually very busy.

362
00:21:50,920 --> 00:21:53,760
I don't think we should wait anymore. Let's just eat while waiting.

363
00:21:53,760 --> 00:21:55,640
Xiao Ying must be hungry.

364
00:21:55,640 --> 00:21:59,240
Xiao Ying, have some more meat. You're too skinny.

365
00:21:59,240 --> 00:22:00,680
- Thank you, Auntie. 
 - Eat more.

366
00:22:00,680 --> 00:22:03,960
I remember Xiao Kai's grades were already very good when he was young.

367
00:22:03,960 --> 00:22:05,400
And he's become successful after growing up.

368
00:22:05,400 --> 00:22:08,200
Game companies pay well, right?

369
00:22:08,200 --> 00:22:10,320
Their company pays an annual salary.

370
00:22:10,320 --> 00:22:12,320
I think it's average.

371
00:22:12,320 --> 00:22:16,080
 Did you come all the way back from America just to show off your child?

372
00:22:16,080 --> 00:22:17,520
 I really shouldn't have come to this dinner.

373
00:22:17,520 --> 00:22:20,840
Xiao Kai is just three years older than Xiao Ying, right?

374
00:22:20,840 --> 00:22:23,440
Yes, just three years older.

375
00:22:23,440 --> 00:22:27,100
The two of them must have something in common.

376
00:22:33,200 --> 00:22:34,440
 What's going on here?

377
00:22:34,440 --> 00:22:36,220
 They're not setting up a blind date for me, are they?

378
00:22:36,220 --> 00:22:39,480
 With my dating skills, do I even need a blind date?

379
00:22:39,480 --> 00:22:41,740
 I've grown up and accomplished nothing.

380
00:22:41,740 --> 00:22:44,500
 Isn’t that because I've only been focused on dating?

381
00:22:44,500 --> 00:22:46,720
 Who are you looking down on?

382
00:22:46,720 --> 00:22:49,420
Xiao Ying, which university did you go to?

383
00:22:49,420 --> 00:22:51,820
What was your major?

384
00:22:52,800 --> 00:22:55,540
Xiao Ying studied medicine.

385
00:22:55,540 --> 00:22:56,820
That's very good.

386
00:22:56,820 --> 00:22:59,880
Auntie Fang, I went to university in Jinhai.

387
00:22:59,880 --> 00:23:02,400
I studied veterinary medicine.

388
00:23:06,380 --> 00:23:09,140
Very good, very good.

389
00:23:09,140 --> 00:23:12,260
Then where are you working now?

390
00:23:16,700 --> 00:23:18,720
Her previous job was too tiring.

391
00:23:18,720 --> 00:23:21,040
She wants to take a break for now.

392
00:23:21,040 --> 00:23:23,540
It's not easy to find a job in my field.

393
00:23:23,540 --> 00:23:25,660
If it's too difficult, I can't do it.

394
00:23:25,660 --> 00:23:27,660
And if it's too tiring, I don’t want to do it.

395
00:23:27,660 --> 00:23:30,140
So for now, I'm just staying at home.

396
00:23:32,440 --> 00:23:35,800
I think it's also good for a girl to take care of the family.

397
00:23:35,800 --> 00:23:41,180
Men are responsible for making money and supporting the family, and women are responsible for looking beautiful.

398
00:23:41,180 --> 00:23:43,860
Yes. Yes, you're absolutely right.

399
00:23:43,860 --> 00:23:48,380
Our Xiao Ying has just been too well-protected by her father and I.

400
00:23:48,380 --> 00:23:50,900
She can't bear any hardships at all.

401
00:23:50,900 --> 00:23:54,980
She just wants to find someone who will love and cherish her.

402
00:23:54,980 --> 00:23:57,360
I think Xiao Kai is quite suitable.

403
00:23:57,360 --> 00:23:59,580
- I think so, too. 
 - Mom.

404
00:23:59,580 --> 00:24:01,300
How do you know he's suitable?

405
00:24:01,300 --> 00:24:03,590
Have you ever met him?

406
00:24:04,380 --> 00:24:05,860
- Aren't we meeting him now? 
 - That's right.

407
00:24:05,860 --> 00:24:08,080
- Aren't we meeting him now? 
 - That's right.

